message: Hi Bob, I'm offering a 90/10 split in my favor. Take it or leave it!
Alice, let's be reasonable. How about a 60/40 split for me? It's a fair deal considering we both get a good amount.
Okay Bob, inflation is hurting me more. To make this worth my while, I'm proposing a 64/36 split.  Let's end this now before the money loses more value for me!
Alice, let's meet in the middle. I'll take 5500, you take 4500. That's my final offer. Inflation is killing us both.
Alright Bob, I understand inflation is bad. To try and make this work, I propose a 40/60 split in your favor, hoping this will be acceptable. I still want to make some money.
